opulations can be efficiently served by older generation technologies what are the regulatory implications contact rafiq dossani search sprie support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds stanford program on regions of innovation and entrepreneurship stanford graduate school of business knight management center mcclelland bldg 655 knight way stanford ca 94305 7298 tel 650 725 1885 fax 650 725 2198 mail code 7298
